channel.title: Taharok's Birthday
channel.description:
Today it's Mod Taharok's 14th Birthday and we all remember all the times that have happened such as him helping fight the spams by cleaning the sections and stuff so i think we should all congratulate and wish him a VERY happy birthday..
Happy Birthday Mod Taharok, Best Wishes
Sir Jay ;)
